This product bundles the public Uruguayan national PKI Certification Authority
certificates (trust anchors) under src/firmauy/data/, used only to
verify signatures against the national root. They are public certificates (not
private keys), issued by AGESIC and the Ministerio del Interior. See
src/firmauy/data/PROVENANCE.md for sources and fingerprints. This
project is not affiliated with or endorsed by AGESIC.
